# ROADMAP funnel (mandatory)

## Sources of truth

| Surface | Role |
|---------|------|
| `docs/ROADMAP.md` | **Now / Next / Later** (≤3 Now, ≤5 Done) |
| GitHub issues | Detail, acceptance criteria, portfolio |
| `.omg/workflow-manifest.json` | Active agent spec/plan packages only |
| `docs/brain_dump.md` | **Retired** — redirect only; do not triage |

## Before any implementation

```bash
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py agent
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py intake "<request>"
```

If intake says `capture_to: later` → update ROADMAP **Later** only; **no code**.

If `requires_planning` → `/work-intake` skill phases 2–3 (`/ralplan`, `/deep-interview`).

```bash
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py approve-impl --issue N
uv run python scripts/roadmap.py gate --request "<request>"   # use --require-allowed if ORBIT_WARS_IMPL_GATE=1
```

## Commands

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `roadmap.py agent` | Status + workflow phases |
| `roadmap.py intake` | Map request → ROADMAP / planning path |
| `roadmap.py approve-impl` | Allow implementation (writes `.omg/state/impl-gate.json`) |
| `roadmap.py clear-impl` | Clear gate after Done |
| `roadmap.py validate` | CI structure checks (bans brain_dump in Now/Next) |

## Git

Commit verified work locally; push only when the user asks.
